Dialogue: 5,0:02:20.74,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Far too weak!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.49,0:02:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.16,0:02:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you straight to Hell.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Messiah Chain!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Captain Japan?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thanks,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Messiah Lady.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Messiah Lady!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better be dead.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.24,0:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not die!
