Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.59,0:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me, foolish humans.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.64,0:03:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the queen of the demon world—
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a messenger from the realm of darkness!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.65,0:03:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a queen {\i1}and{\i0} a messenger?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.62,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The heinous ESPer Idol,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Todoroki Amane!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't twirl so excitedly, or...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel... dizzy...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.34,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Charged to the max!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.05,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilianne!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.17,0:04:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoopsie-daisie!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.52,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Heinous and cruel, I am on the prowl!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your continued support!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too drastic a personality shift.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up:
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,my evil underling,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat Man!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This premise really is pushing it...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.82,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But as long as we're doing this, \Nwe've gotta do it right!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As bland as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bland cat.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat Man ESP:
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bang!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.07,0:04:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Teleportation magic!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.92,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall repent!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beat.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lilianne! Don't do this to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to take it from here, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the cutey-lovely Hironacchi!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.37,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.23,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
