Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That was weird.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen way better stuff on TV.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.15,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the "ESPer Idol Amanel" magic show!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We look forward to seeing you again!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't the least bit special, Hasudou.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.66,0:06:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,While she might have been weak, she was capable of using multiple abilities, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.61,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That sets her apart from \Nnormal ESPers like you, Aya.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.37,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The estimated value of her potential abilities is abnormally high.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Much higher than anything I've seen before.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's accurate?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.50,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's with this stuffed toy that supplies her with power?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.69,0:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Todoroki Amane, you're irresistible.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.09,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aya, let's use test subject number fourteen in the special show we're inviting her to.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She might die, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll cross that bridge when we come to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.84,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat that too...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.81,0:07:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You never can use it without my help, can you?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.01,0:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know that already, then don't bail on me partway through, Lilianne!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.44,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, we need to discuss the steady decline in attendance.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the whole "heinous"\N thing was a bad idea.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.59,0:08:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Need I remind you how the \Nstandard idol act went?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the "idol" part's the problem here.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, why don't you take the stage with us, Nanae-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.47,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Esperanza Magic" was a really cool name.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! What is that, Amane-chan?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well... that was...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she kinda freaky?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped the car using my powers.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have a problem?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.83,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She possesses a power \Nsimilar to ours, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.30,0:09:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she covered for us.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.02,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This power tends to scare people,\N so I should try not to use it too much.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it felt different today.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.36,0:09:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was one with you, Amane.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.49,0:09:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a part of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt a little good,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.08,0:09:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but if we do that again, \Nyou'll lose all your friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.28,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd be better off \Nwithout me around.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.14,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my little sister.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're twins!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.76,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I really stay with you?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.96,0:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.26,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Lilianne.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stay together forever.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.67,0:09:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When I found out that the lady who saved me was using her powers to hold magic shows,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was awesome!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was amazed that these powers could be used like that!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Time for special training!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to learn some crazy technique.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.72,0:10:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll learn to fly like Messiah Lady, even!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.26,Alternative,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!{lily}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.71,0:10:17.63,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Stop!{lily}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll be overnight sensations!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it'll be that easy.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too naïve, Amane-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There he goes again.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazukicchi and his "Nope-Nope" disease.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, am I wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We can totally do this!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.24,0:10:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We have your transportation abilities
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.11,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and Hironacchi's superhuman strength.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do our best, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.86,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lilianne's...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's Lilianne you're worried about?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you fallen for her?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.70,0:10:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.49,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, once we put on shows \Nthat are a lot more fun
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and convince people that they don't need to be afraid of ISH,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we won't have to keep a low profile anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.87,0:10:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love for that to happen too.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.09,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, we have to capture the \Naudience's hearts by using proper magic.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it now?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This really {\i1}does{\i0} call for special training!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.97,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Lilianne.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see you later!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not even listening to me...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Now I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.54,sentimental takagi,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.1\fad(0,500)\blur0.8\frz359.4\fscx148\fscy116\move(612,271,611.34,368.65,27,2738)}S{*\c&H3F152C&}e{*\c&H3E142B&}n{*\c&H3D132B&}t{*\c&H3C132A&}i{*\c&H3B1229&}m{*\c&H3A1129&}e{*\c&H391028&}n{\c&H381028&}t {\c&H2C0D22&}T{*\c&H250B1F&}a{\c&H1E0A1C&}k{*\c&H1E091B&}a{*\c&H1F081A&}g{\c&H20081A&}i
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You reek of booze.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here for training advice again?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.54,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any special \Ntraining methods for flying?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.94,0:11:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a tough one.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Five thousand yen.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Make it five hundred \Nand you've got a deal.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on a second.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.15,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact Gaia right away.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now convey to you Gaia's will.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This should do the trick!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it won't.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.82,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.85,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Belief is the key to your ISH abilities.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.58,0:12:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone like you, foolish enough to believe the most barefaced of lies, anything is possible.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.79,0:12:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane may be a fool, \Nbut this is really pushing it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds hard.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, foolish girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.25,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be five hundred yen.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're still going to charge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:37.44,epititlezode,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.33\blur1\bord0\b1\fscx28\fscy28\frz19.32\pos(881,96)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H26&}CROQUETTES
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.72,0:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we should do some \Nteleportation training.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.06,0:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We only ever use it unconsciously.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-second rule...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-second rule.{>it's wrapped in paper}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.00,0:12:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Todoroki Amane from the \Nperforming troupe "Nought," right?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but who are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, could you be a fan of mine?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.62,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought as much.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who are—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.64,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your magic's bogus, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call it bogus!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it isn't—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.10,Alternative,,0,0,0,,It's ISH...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.10,0:13:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?{i like the concept here that the magic is fake because it's real}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same as you.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you saying you're an ESPer too?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Also...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I-A-M.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.49,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I.A.M?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've heard of it?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.91,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Their popularity has gone \Nthrough the roof recently.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I.A.M's Cruel Illusion:
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.50,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a spectacle of bloodshed and insanity!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.30,0:13:46.34,Bloodshed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\shad3\blur1.5\clip(m 104 508 l 1074 665 1147 153 355 -154)\org(1694,1052)\frx4.2\fry9.5\fscx65\fscy115\4c&H4B368E&\move(1302.85,415.988,981.703,419.417,21,350)\c&H450EE5&}Can you handle this spectacle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:46.34,Bloodshed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\shad3\blur1.5\org(1694,1052)\frx4.2\fry9.5\clip(m 104 508 l 1074 665 1147 153 355 -154)\fscx64\fscy109\c&H2F11E5&\4c&H4B368E&\move(1305.14,613.714,976,604.571,26,410)}of bloodshed and insanity?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.26,0:13:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I haven't seen it, \Nsince I can't stand scary stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.84,Bloodshed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur8\org(1694,1052)\frx4.2\fry9.5\clip(m 104 508 l 1074 665 1147 153 355 -154)\c&HE9BEEA&\move(1222.29,562.285,952.857,566.571,20,1605)\1a&H16&}Not for the faint of heart!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.84,Bloodshed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur1.2\org(1694,1052)\frx4.2\fry9.5\clip(m 104 508 l 1074 665 1147 153 355 -154)\c&HEEDAF0&\move(1222.29,562.285,952.857,566.571,20,1605)\1a&H16&}N{\c&HE1BBE2&}o{\c&HD8A2DA&}t {\c&HEACEE6&}f{\c&HEEDAF0&}o{\c&HE1BBE2&}r {\c&HD8A2DA&}t{\c&HEACEE6&}h{\c&HEEDAF0&}e {\c&HE1BBE2&}f{\c&HD8A2DA&}a{\c&HEACEE6&}i{\c&HEEDAF0&}n{\c&HE1BBE2&}t {\c&HD8A2DA&}o{\c&HEACEE6&}f {\c&HEEDAF0&}h{\c&HE1BBE2&}e{\c&HD8A2DA&}a{\c&HEACEE6&}r{\c&HEEDAF0&}t{\c&HE1BBE2&}!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.64,0:13:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you be Aya-chan,\N I.A.M's masked magician?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, could you tag along with me?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.86,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.95,0:14:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to a special show.{i'll invite you}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.03,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.28,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{part b 1407}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.93,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanel, Amanel...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanel, Amanel, Amanel, Amanel...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanel!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She left for the day already.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sennokura-sensei?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.38,0:14:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}She worked so hard on the manuscripts this week \Nbecause she was looking forward to seeing Amane-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.05,0:14:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Date!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.32,0:14:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Horror movie!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Haunted house!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane finds that kind of stuff...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...so scary she could cry, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.06,0:14:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But she can't turn down my requests since I'm her patron! So cute!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you \Ncheck out I.A.M's show?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a look.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.47,0:14:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That Aya girl has an ISH ability.{ISH ESPer}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, she seems a tad dangerous.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.79,0:15:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like she's somewhat murderous, bloodthirsty, and bewitching!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably best not to get involved.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you have nothing in common,\N including popularity.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.85,0:15:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is kinda scary...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think Aya-chan's ISH ability is?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.81,0:15:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that weird thing that showed up out of your croquette earlier?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.34,0:15:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, which brings out the devil in men.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The onset of a sinister night.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared already!{lol dat face}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.95,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is deception, and everything is false.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear is the only reality.{truth}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.23,0:16:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's first sacrificial lamb—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.61,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her back!{ugh. use her or it?}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take{\i0} her back.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maximize your ISH output and do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.91,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, I'll rip your precious bear to shreds.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you don't mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.13,0:16:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't hold back.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.38,0:16:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood drops keep falling on my head,\N falling on my head...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so much fun to stab and chop with a knife...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.60,0:16:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chop, chop, mush, mush, la la la!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.77,0:16:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilianne!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ability sucks!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are utterly pathetic \Nwithout your stuffed toy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.99,0:17:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, my ability primarily deals in visual interference.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.43,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're seeing right now\N is an illusion I created.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goes for that thing at the back.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.77,0:17:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But your poor teddy bear's fate...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,was also an illusion!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give her back.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilianne!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.55,0:17:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, will you show me your ISH powers at full strength?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.99,0:17:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.60,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I want to use ISH for\N is to entertain people.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.07,0:17:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.01,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everyone to realize that ISH is an\N amazing power that can be used for fun things!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to understand that it's nothing to be afraid of!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.37,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Scaring the non-ESPers to death is where the real fun lies!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're completely powerless, but they act like they're better
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,just because they outnumber us!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When they find out about our powers,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.64,0:18:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,they get all scared and attack us \Neven if we've done nothing at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up that carefree attitude, \Nand you'll wind up dead one day.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you say.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Amane-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mana-chan?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoohoo!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrificial lamb number two!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't leave what\N few fans you have to die!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope for your sake that \Nthe next one's an illusion too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozu-chan?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your opponent's over there.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.47,0:18:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A non-ESPer who's had \Nhis ISH forcibly awakened.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.18,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thing is, the only way to find out what abilities someone will have, or their potency, is to try it!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is ISH, huh?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.95,0:19:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Two other teensy problems are mental instability and the powers going out of control.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Whoa, this is seriously awesome!{ooo maji sugee}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, number fourteen.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your prey is this girl right here.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maximize your ISH output \Nand get your hands on her.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.71,0:19:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goes for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no rules.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even care if one of you dies.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.51,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The laws we have right now can't touch an ISH ESPer, anyway.{after all}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.89,0:19:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My prey's a high school girl? \NYou really know where it's at.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.61,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to, princess?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.19,0:19:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilianne!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare lay a finger on Kozu-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.87,0:19:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanel?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.99,0:19:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I was told I'd get to see a\N{\alpha&HFF&}...{\r}special show of Amanel's, and then...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.17,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is this?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's so tough!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you could \Ndo this kinda shit too!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.01,0:20:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This power is just so damn amusing!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.76,0:20:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanel!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.11,0:20:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozu-chan...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane, are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.91,0:20:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a magic show?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She really {\i1}is{\i0} nothing special.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and run away!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.45,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No!{iya da}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.77,0:20:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Warp!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.68,0:20:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Warp! Warp!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself, Amane.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.11,0:21:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember all those days you spent training.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it goes.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of luck with your training.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be two hundred yen.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.41,0:21:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll warp for sure!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it, Lilia—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:13.12,epititlezode,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur0.6\bord0\pos(929,416)\frz6.484\fscx22\fscy22\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H52&}HERE
Dialogue: 5,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Warp, warp, warp, warp...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.58,0:21:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Warp!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wha—
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.51,0:21:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so much fun!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Lilianne?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he going berserk?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane, let's become one.{GATTAI}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.87,0:22:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Become one?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like we did back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:15.11,0:22:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you all of my power.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.81,0:22:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilianne...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:20.48,0:22:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep Kozu-chan safe at all costs.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.27,0:22:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:28.11,0:22:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear her voice, but I can feel it.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel every last bit of Lilianne.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:34.35,0:22:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I won't lose!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:36.33,0:22:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... Amanel?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:52.72,0:22:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the heck is that?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:59.44,0:23:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting to the death is the best!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:35.39,0:23:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off already!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:50.82,0:23:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:51.82,0:23:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozu-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:59.54,0:24:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he jump all the way\N up here with the car?!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:06.50,0:24:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to put you through \Nsuch a harrowing experience.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:09.84,0:24:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:11.30,0:24:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:13.38,0:24:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure you reach the end of the show \Nwith a smile on your face!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:22.10,0:24:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:23.91,0:24:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to teleport to the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:25.90,0:24:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my only option.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:27.40,0:24:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,With Liliane's help, I can do this!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:30.49,0:24:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Combine both of our powers into one...{BY YOUR POWERS COMBINED, I AM CAPTAIN JAPAN}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:34.49,0:24:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Warp!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:35.57,0:24:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To the sea!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:51.42,0:24:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilianne?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:53.47,0:24:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:54.82,0:24:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:56.64,0:24:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there...
Dialogue: 5,0:24:58.10,0:25:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there for just a little longer.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:07.06,0:25:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all righ—
Dialogue: 5,0:25:16.63,0:25:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... saved.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:23.75,0:25:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:25.74,0:25:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:27.54,0:25:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't Amanel's show a \Nsimple magic performance?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:40.30,0:25:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozu-chan,
Dialogue: 5,0:25:41.47,0:25:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,stay calm and hear me out.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:44.68,0:25:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It talk—
Dialogue: 5,0:25:45.73,0:25:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't come to hate Amane.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:49.02,0:25:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's doing all of this for my sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:51.65,0:25:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Amane's twin {kid }sister,
Dialogue: 5,0:25:54.36,0:25:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't have a body.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:56.62,0:25:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a body?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:58.32,0:26:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently I lost it while I was still in my mother's womb.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:02.23,0:26:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I have \Nis this strange power.{Lilianne's Bizarre Power}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:05.96,0:26:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, Amane wants me to feel like I belong in this world.{it's okay for me to be here}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:10.13,0:26:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to give my life \Na meaning—a purpose.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:13.05,0:26:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she puts on those magic shows.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:18.13,0:26:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 5,0:26:21.85,0:26:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe me.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:23.64,0:26:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane would never use \Nthis power for herself.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:28.27,0:26:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She may be a fool, \Nbut she's a really honest one.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:31.48,0:26:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 5,0:26:33.32,0:26:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So please believe in Amane!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:35.74,0:26:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please don't come to hate her!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:39.09,0:26:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:43.53,0:26:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:44.79,0:26:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:46.62,0:26:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure this show has a happy ending!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:51.29,0:26:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Honest and foolish...
Dialogue: 5,0:26:53.88,0:26:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I get why Amanel's shows are so fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:58.42,0:26:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:59.63,0:27:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget coming to hate her,
Dialogue: 5,0:27:01.59,0:27:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an even bigger fan of hers now!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:05.93,0:27:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:14.86,0:27:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I hear laughter.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:19.70,0:27:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That, and this restless noise...{nagi translator: noisy noise}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:25.24,0:27:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the waves?
Dialogue: 5,0:27:27.20,0:27:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Or could it be applause?
Dialogue: 5,0:27:37.61,0:27:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at this power.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:40.15,0:27:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:42.43,0:27:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Todoroki Amane is an Archetype—\Nbeings that were said to have gone extinct!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:48.18,0:27:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:50.43,0:27:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea where she is \Nor what she's up to.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:53.44,0:27:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasudou did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.95,0:28:08.37,ED-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Massugu na omoi dake ga
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.95,0:28:08.37,ED-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}If only the most honest of emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.37,0:28:12.16,ED-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Hikari ni nareru nara
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.37,0:28:12.16,ED-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Can become the shining light
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.58,0:28:17.71,ED-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Taisetsu na hito no tame
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.58,0:28:17.71,ED-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Then I'll become a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.71,0:28:20.59,ED-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Kage ni naru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.71,0:28:20.59,ED-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}For the ones I hold dear
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.80,0:28:30.06,ED-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Onaji katachi no heart mottetemo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.80,0:28:30.06,ED-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}While our hearts may all look the same
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.23,0:28:37.82,ED-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Kokoro asymmetry
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.23,0:28:37.82,ED-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Our souls are asymmetrical
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.32,0:28:42.86,ED-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Namida de balance no
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.32,0:28:42.86,ED-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Once we use our tears
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.86,0:28:46.57,ED-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Kusari hodokeba
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.86,0:28:46.57,ED-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}To break free from the shackles of conformity
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.16,0:28:51.87,ED-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Mou daijoubu kanashimi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.16,0:28:51.87,ED-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}We will be just fine
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.54,0:28:55.58,ED-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Chikara ni kawaru
